WEBVTT

00:00.219 --> 00:01.219
<i>Previously on "Heartland":</i>

00:01.321 --> 00:02.220
Hey, I'm back.

00:02.288 --> 00:03.022
Shane?

00:03.023 --> 00:04.656
When're you gonna
talk to him?

00:04.724 --> 00:06.358
You know, maybe for once,
you should just...

00:06.426 --> 00:07.493
Try not to interfere.

00:07.560 --> 00:08.594
Look at you and Amy.

00:08.661 --> 00:09.828
You guys are sorta
back together,

00:09.896 --> 00:11.062
but neither one of you

00:11.130 --> 00:12.197
are saying you're actually
back together.

00:12.265 --> 00:13.632
We're closer than
we've ever been before.

00:13.700 --> 00:14.767
So, in that respect,

00:14.834 --> 00:16.134
yes,
we're back together.

00:16.202 --> 00:18.002
I'd love to go
and show Renard

00:18.069 --> 00:20.405
what I can do with Spartan
once...

00:20.472 --> 00:22.239
Once I can actually do
something.

00:22.307 --> 00:24.842
We're you planning on
telling me you're moving out?

00:24.910 --> 00:26.944
This is not Amy
and I breaking up, Jack.

00:27.012 --> 00:28.446
I think it's time
to take it to another level.

00:36.353 --> 00:37.421
(Horse whinnies)

00:40.858 --> 00:42.325
(Spartan nickers)

00:46.330 --> 00:47.930
