Yeah, he looks good.

07:01.247 --> 07:02.281
He looks real good.

07:02.348 --> 07:04.116
I just can't help
but wonder...

07:04.184 --> 07:07.286
What I did to deserve
such an extravagant gift?

07:07.353 --> 07:10.255
Well, he's not exactly
a gift, Tim.

07:10.323 --> 07:11.856
More like a business deal.

07:11.924 --> 07:13.925
I'm a jockey;
I can't legally own a horse.

07:13.993 --> 07:15.159
I need a partner.

07:15.227 --> 07:16.627
So why me?

07:16.695 --> 07:18.196
Well, maybe off the track,

07:18.263 --> 07:20.798
our relationship didn't
turn out so great.

07:20.865 --> 07:22.600
But on the track?

07:22.667 --> 07:24.203
We made a hell
of a team.

07:24.267 --> 07:25.703
Who better to
hook up with?

07:25.770 --> 07:27.805
Well, I mean,
he looks promising.

07:27.872 --> 07:29.240
There's no doubt
about that.

07:29.308 --> 07:31.374
You know me,
I can't pass up a good deal.

07:31.442 --> 07:32.942
So that means?

07:33.010 --> 07:34.077
That means nothing.
Not yet.

07:34.145 --> 07:35.912
Not until Scott
looks at him.

07:35.980 --> 07:37.214
You'd be a fool
to agree to anything

07:37.281 --> 07:38.548
without getting him vetted.

07:38.616 --> 07:40.250
Yeah, and a lawyer--
to look at the paperwork,

07:40.318 --> 07:42.051
make sure
everything's legal.

07:42.120 --> 07:43.786
Hey, yeah, sure.

07:43.854 --> 07:46.989
It's all gotta be
above board.

07:47.056 --> 07:50.058
And Amy,
I want her involved.

07:50.127 --> 07:52.794
<i>She really came through for me</i>
<i>with Dexter.</i>

07:52.862 --> 07:53.895
Right. You mean,

07:53.963 --> 07:55.731
when she turned him
into a jumper?

07:57.300 --> 07:58.567
Not a good start.

07:58.635 --> 08:00.037
(Snorted chuckle)

08:00.135 --> 08:02.637
Sure. Amy. Of course.

08:03.905 --> 08:05.406
Hey, Lou.

08:05.474 --> 08:08.276
Yeah, and how's
my favourite niece?

08:09.178 --> 08:10.978
Okay, okay...

08:11.046 --> 08:12.547
Yup.

08:12.615 --> 08:14.549
Mm-hm.
And the in-laws?

08:15.518 --> 08:18.285
Oh, okay.
No, I understand. I do.

08:18.353 --> 08:19.219
You know what?

08:19.287 --> 08:21.121
I'm gonna call you back
after dinner though.

08:21.189 --> 08:22.256
Okay.

08:22.323 --> 08:23.923
Yeah. Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Bye.

08:23.991 --> 08:25.292
Geez,
she's in a good mood.

08:25.360 --> 08:27.027
Mmm...

08:27.094 --> 08:28.594
Expecting someone?

08:28.662 --> 08:30.363
For example, Ty?

08:31.298 --> 08:32.232
Uh...

08:32.399 --> 08:34.799
No. It's just got distracted
talking to Lou.

08:36.270 --> 08:37.837
(Door closes)

08:37.905 --> 08:39.238
Tim:
Hello!

08:39.306 --> 08:41.573
Amy: Hey.
Tim: Mmm, beef stew...

08:41.642 --> 08:44.442
Huh, somebody must've been
reading my mind.

08:44.510 --> 08:45.544
Anybody sitting here?

08:45.611 --> 08:49.014
So, Tim,
what brings you by?

08:49.082 --> 08:50.749
You know,
other than dinner?

08:50.817 --> 08:53.185
<i>Tim:</i> <i>Well, I have a
favour</i> <i>to ask... you.</i>

08:53.252 --> 08:55.220
- Uh-huh.
- It's about a horse.

08:55.288 --> 08:56.655
- Okay.
- I'd like you to look at him.

08:56.723 --> 08:58.824
He's a two-year-old,
hasn't run his first race yet.

08:58.892 --> 09:02.093
Race? What, you're talking
about a racehorse?

09:02.161 --> 09:03.961
Yeah, not just any racehorse,
Jack.

09:04.029 --> 09:05.396
We're talking about a horse
that's gonna put me back

09:05.463 --> 09:06.798
in the winners' circle.

09:06.865 --> 09:09.100
Yeah.

09:09.168 --> 09:10.568
(Crickets chirp)

09:18.676 --> 09:19.743
(Phone rings)

09:25.549 --> 09:27.050
Hey.

09:27.118 --> 09:28.451
<i>Amy:</i> <i>Yeah, I kinda
missed you</i> <i>at dinner.</i>

09:28.519 --> 09:31.054
And it's weird not seeing
lights on in the barn.

09:31.122 --> 09:33.789
Yeah. It's gonna take
a while to get used to.

09:33.857 --> 09:35.524
Yeah, it must be weird.

09:35.592 --> 09:36.926
Be so quiet,

09:36.993 --> 09:38.728
after living four years
above a horse barn.

09:38.795 --> 09:40.662
(Animal chatters)

09:40.731 --> 09:42.898
Actually,
it's kinda noisy.

09:42.966 --> 09:44.033
(Laughs)

09:45.301 --> 09:46.301
(Animal chatters loudly)

09:46.369 --> 09:47.703
Hey, Amy?

09:47.770 --> 09:49.838
Um, I'm gonna have
to call you back, okay?

09:49.905 --> 09:51.272
Oh. Okay.

09:51.340 --> 09:53.141
Bye.
(Phone beeps off)

09:54.076 --> 09:56.144
(Animal chatters nearby)

